Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.45,0:01:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味佳餚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味佳餚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺他們好像來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重振士氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽好 沖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真癢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的攻擊對他們完全無效嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像起了雞皮疙瘩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻笑就給我到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還是和以前一樣白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你也夠嗆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那種拖後腿的小鬼一起執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣 水木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你別再做這種傻事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你又打算背叛村裏的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起同甘共苦的木葉村同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是很天真啊 伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只相信力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想用那種無聊羈絆束縛我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將得到最強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候 我一定會讓你明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些木葉忍者口中所謂的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多麼荒謬無聊的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事發生之前 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很優秀的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說的好像自己什麼都懂一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 所有的攻擊都被化解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你這麼說了 那就讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對同伴的眷念到底有多深
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能阻止我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管這些傢伙了 快去追水木吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回來一定好好跟你們算這筆帳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 那個傢伙好像走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像大家都走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 難道他們在捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏 捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 我們倆是鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙 擅自就下決定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發 雷神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,新生三人組 兩人加一只
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回可別被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話 想質疑我再等一百年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣慢慢吞吞 又會有麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間對付這些傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 捉迷藏很好玩啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我肚子好像餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法 雷神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了給哥哥留點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩只白癡兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有言在先 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這兩個傢伙鬥根本沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事早知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木 你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來阻止我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再做蠢事了 水木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我出來 水木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時不時就要關注背後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是作為一個忍者基本中的基本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是伊魯卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻要讀取敵人內心的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是作為一個忍者基本中的基本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話 應該我來說才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煙霧彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 來抓我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 又變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷神 這簡直是超級捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調虎離山啊 真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該能多爭取些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個綱手婆婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指不可思議的怪力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會如此沉醉於力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為力量才是全部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再仔細考慮考慮 水木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在回頭還不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒搞清自己的處境嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 放馬過來啊 伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我的敵人 是村裏的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經厭倦這種說法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你和我都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣是繼承著火之意志的木葉成員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以別再做蠢事了 水木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個說法讓我更惱火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來看在昔日的情分上 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你死得痛快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我快活快活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你感覺一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被所謂的同伴慢慢折磨至死的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你打算等到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他們發現只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他們了 在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 又是超級捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像玩膩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是影分身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還是沒想出什麼好辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暈頭轉向了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 幹得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好難受 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在 抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 笨蛋怪力兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中 思想集中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝酷了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是比我還差的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都比我優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是被你幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在笑容下暗藏著悲傷 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你一直是大家的開心果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有悲傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者在任務中以身殉職是件光榮的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是爸爸還是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了保護村子不惜犧牲性命的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是英雄的後代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一個人也不會悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是高興的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你一直獨自承受悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你並不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉村所有的忍者都繼承了火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想保護木葉村的強烈意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有了這種火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以村裏的每個人都是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡 你也擁有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說伊魯卡最近無精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常擔心 所以就來找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很擔心你哦 伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在那邊等著呢 一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所認識的水木是個溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比誰都體貼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快清醒過來吧 水木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 雷神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我踩到盒飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話 給我乖乖待在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還我便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你好像還不知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你這麼體貼的真正原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看到你那悲慘的背影 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比什麼都快樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家打算一起踢足球 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡也來參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了那種事 伊魯卡沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們必須好好鼓勵鼓勵他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼眼裏只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母被九尾殺了所以倍受關愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連火影大人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 到底為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我也來討好火影大人一回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說伊魯卡最近無精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俯視比自己弱小的人感覺很痛快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說你太天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種天真會讓你在戰場上喪命的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰場上能殺幾個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在竹林裏使用苦無
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半會被竹子弄得偏離軌道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想命中目標的話 只有直接攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會再上當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏對我不利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道會偏離的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就提前計算好偏移量再攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你總算認真了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你總算醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟蹋了我們的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想就這麼算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答這個問題還真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個任務的超級救援部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉村的最強組合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬鹿蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的怪力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然憑藉蠻力和影子模仿術抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在術被解開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會對我們很不利的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來必須做個了結了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:22:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:22:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂 新陣形 豬鹿蝶
